reviews.review_text: Nice FM source ! I wondered when this source would surface and since it's a true FM source it probably will be eligible for download !  I had a 3rd gen cassette copy of the second set; this source is a nice upgrade for a great show ! A well played  pre drums segment with one of the best Foolish Heart I've ever heard !  Spring 1990 was a great tour because the GD was hauling a 24 track around for a Live LP release later known as "without a net" Grab this one if you want some great Spring 90 GD !!!
